{
  "_authoring_notes": [
    "Phase 4b-hub Section 3 — 2x2 Community grid (Mortgage Finance / Financial Services Law / Real Estate / Property Preservation).",
    "Per Jonathan's flow-correction directive (2026-04-28):",
    "  - Communities are BROADER than memberships. Cards must NOT show membership logos or subtitles (NMSA & MSEA / LEGAL LEAGUE / FORCE / PPEF) — that conflates Step 2 of the audience flow (community identification) with Step 4 (specialty membership).",
    "  - Card body copy describes the COMMUNITY (the practitioners + their lifecycle role), not the membership orgs.",
    "  - Callouts use 'Where ...' parallel structure to convey each community's lifecycle handoff role (not what the profession 'does' — readers know what they do).",
    "  - CTAs say 'Learn More' (single verb, parallel across cards) per Jonathan's preference.",
    "  - Anchor event chips drop month suffixes (no '· Apr', '· Sept', '· May · New Orleans') — cleaner row, removes the redundant Sept appearing on all cards.",
    "Card alignment via flex-column + min-height per row element + margin-top:auto on CTA — guarantees title / body / callout / chips / CTA all align across the row regardless of body length variation.",
    "CTA routing:",
    "  Mortgage Finance / Financial Services Law / Property Preservation → /communities/ parent stub (Phase 4b 2nd-instance pages will resolve these)",
    "  Real Estate → /communities/real-estate-professionals/ (live ✅)",
    "Anchor event chip routing:",
    "  LLSS → /events/legal-league-servicer-summit/ (live ✅)",
    "  Velocity → /events/velocity/ (live ✅)",
    "  Government Forum → external https://www.fivestargovernmentforum.com/2026",
    "  Five Star Conference → external https://www.fivestarconference.com/2026",
    "Callout uses FSI-kit-conforming pattern: offwhite bg + 4px gold left-border + navy italic text (matches RE Pros page Section 4 Founding Institutional Partner callout)."
