      "settings": {
        "html": "<div style=\"max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto;\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); gap:24px;\">\n\n    <!-- 01 MORTGAGE FINANCE -->\n    <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:3px solid #1f365c; border-radius:6px; padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:'Roboto Slab', Georgia, serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#1f365c; text-transform:none; letter-spacing:-0.2px; margin:0 0 20px;\">Mortgage Finance</h3>\n      <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:130px;\">Servicers, subservicers, mortgage bankers, and lenders. The professionals who manage every home loan in America from origination through resolution &mdash; and whose portfolio decisions trigger every other community's work.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:#f7f7f5; border-left:4px solid #c9a040; border-radius:0 4px 4px 0; padding:14px 16px; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:84px; display:flex; align-items:center;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; font-style:italic; margin:0;\">Where the portfolio decisions are made that engage every other profession.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px; min-height:42px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.fivestargovernmentforum.com/2026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Government Forum</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.fivestarconference.com/2026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Five Star Conference</a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto;\">\n        <a href=\"/communities/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border:2px solid #1f365c; border-radius:4px; padding:10px 24px; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Learn More &rarr;</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 02 FINANCIAL SERVICES LAW -->\n    <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:3px solid #1f365c; border-radius:6px; padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:'Roboto Slab', Georgia, serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#1f365c; text-transform:none; letter-spacing:-0.2px; margin:0 0 20px;\">Financial Services Law</h3>\n      <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:130px;\">Foreclosure, bankruptcy, and mortgage servicing law practitioners. The legal architecture that moves non-performing assets through every stage of resolution &mdash; at the speed and accuracy the lifecycle requires.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:#f7f7f5; border-left:4px solid #c9a040; border-radius:0 4px 4px 0; padding:14px 16px; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:84px; display:flex; align-items:center;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; font-style:italic; margin:0;\">Where law turns servicer decisions into resolution.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px; min-height:42px;\">\n        <a href=\"/events/legal-league-servicer-summit/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">LLSS</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.fivestarconference.com/2026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Five Star Conference</a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto;\">\n        <a href=\"/communities/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border:2px solid #1f365c; border-radius:4px; padding:10px 24px; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Learn More &rarr;</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 03 REAL ESTATE -->\n    <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:3px solid #1f365c; border-radius:6px; padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:'Roboto Slab', Georgia, serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#1f365c; text-transform:none; letter-spacing:-0.2px; margin:0 0 20px;\">Real Estate</h3>\n      <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:130px;\">Agents, brokers, REO specialists, SFR investors, and property managers. The professionals who return distressed and institutional inventory to productive use &mdash; and close the housing lifecycle.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:#f7f7f5; border-left:4px solid #c9a040; border-radius:0 4px 4px 0; padding:14px 16px; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:84px; display:flex; align-items:center;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; font-style:italic; margin:0;\">Where assets return to productive use and the lifecycle closes.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px; min-height:42px;\">\n        <a href=\"/events/velocity/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Velocity</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.fivestarconference.com/2026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Five Star Conference</a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto;\">\n        <a href=\"/communities/real-estate-professionals/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border:2px solid #1f365c; border-radius:4px; padding:10px 24px; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Learn More &rarr;</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 04 PROPERTY PRESERVATION -->\n    <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:3px solid #1f365c; border-radius:6px; padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:'Roboto Slab', Georgia, serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#1f365c; text-transform:none; letter-spacing:-0.2px; margin:0 0 20px;\">Property Preservation</h3>\n      <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:130px;\">National field services and rehabilitation specialists. The professionals who maintain and restore assets between servicer decision and market disposition &mdash; protecting value at every stage.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:#f7f7f5; border-left:4px solid #c9a040; border-radius:0 4px 4px 0; padding:14px 16px; margin:0 0 20px; min-height:84px; display:flex; align-items:center;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:14px; line-height:1.55; font-style:italic; margin:0;\">Where value is preserved between servicer decision and market disposition.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:20px; min-height:42px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.fivestarconference.com/2026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#fff; color:#1f365c; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:20px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;\">Five Star Conference</a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:auto;\">\n        <a href=\"/communities/\" style=\"display:inline-block; background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border:2px solid #1f365c; border-radius:4px; padding:10px 24px; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; text-decoration:none; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Learn More &rarr;</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
      },
